<BlogPost
  title="How to manage CLAUDE.md files across multiple projects without going insane"
  description="Freelancers, agency devs, and indie hackers juggle 5-15 projects. Each needs its own CLAUDE.md. Here is a practical system for managing them all without copy-paste chaos."
